    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genus containing 5 species of trees in the mahogany family Meliaceae, native from Afghanistan south to India, and east to North Korea, Papua New Guinea and eastern Australia.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
